"{\"uid\": \"joe.co.uk-news-teammate-of-convicted-child-rapist-says-hes-disappointed-at-reaction-at-paris-olympics-451591\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Play the JOE Pub Quiz  Share  Published12:28 2 Aug 2024 BST  The volleyball partner of convicted child rapist Steven van de Velde has spoken out in defence of his teammate after he received boos and jeers from the crowd at the Olympic Games in Paris.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 250, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 56, \"end\": 59, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Summer_Time\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.276248714905016e-22, \"text\": \"BST\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Summer_Time\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Summer_Time\"}, {\"begin\": 117, \"end\": 129, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charles_William_Meredith_van_de_Velde\", \"score\": 0.9999786743697067, \"rank\": 2.1326084920168366e-05, \"text\": \"van de Velde\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charles_William_Meredith_van_de_Velde\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charles_William_Meredith_van_de_Velde\"}, {\"begin\": 244, \"end\": 249, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.999999999996362, \"rank\": 3.638395169234674e-12, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The pair, who represent the Netherlands, received a hostile reception from the audience when they took their place in the center of the arena for their first match against Italian pair Alex Ranghieri and Adrian Carambula and the criticism has only intensified in subsequent games.\", \"from\": 252, \"to\": 532, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 280, \"end\": 291, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\", \"score\": 0.7305848271033489, \"rank\": 0.3687652235812949, \"text\": \"Netherlands\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\"}, {\"begin\": 424, \"end\": 431, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italian_language\", \"score\": 0.9198991819772157, \"rank\": 0.08121100026508385, \"text\": \"Italian\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italian_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italian_language\"}, {\"begin\": 437, \"end\": 451, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Ranghieri\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Alex Ranghieri\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q15117302\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Ranghieri\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Ranghieri\"}, {\"begin\": 456, \"end\": 472, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adrian_Carambula\", \"score\": 0.9999915427795907, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Adrian Carambula\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q15117302\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adrian_Carambula\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adrian_Carambula\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Boos -and some applause - as Steven van de Velde, who was convicted of raping a 12-year-old British girl when he was 19, enters the Stadium with his partner Matthew Immers.\", \"from\": 534, \"to\": 706, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 570, \"end\": 582, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charles_William_Meredith_van_de_Velde\", \"score\": 0.9999786743697067, \"rank\": 2.1326084920168366e-05, \"text\": \"van de Velde\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charles_William_Meredith_van_de_Velde\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charles_William_Meredith_van_de_Velde\"}, {\"begin\": 626, \"end\": 633, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9999994513747565, \"rank\": 5.448507284248486e-07, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The boos were more audible when he was later introduced separately#PARIS2024pic.twitter.com/yJGjxXKzE9  Van de Velde was convicted of raping a 12-year-old when he was 19.\", \"from\": 707, \"to\": 877, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The athlete, now 29, received a four year sentence in 2016.\", \"from\": 879, \"to\": 938, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He admitted three counts of rape against a child during an incident which took place in August 2014.\", \"from\": 940, \"to\": 1040, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He had met the British girl on Facebook and flown to England to meet her with full knowledge of her age, theGuardianreported.\", \"from\": 1042, \"to\": 1167, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1057, \"end\": 1064, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9999994513747565, \"rank\": 5.448507284248486e-07, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 1095, \"end\": 1102, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/England_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999985448168119, \"rank\": 8.338528591671348e-07, \"text\": \"England\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/England_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/England_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The athlete only served 12 months of his sentence before he was released.\", \"from\": 1169, \"to\": 1242, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"His teammate, Matthew Immers said he was 'disappointed' by the fans reaction that Van de Velde has received.\", \"from\": 1244, \"to\": 1352, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He said: \\\"I do not want to say much about it.\", \"from\": 1354, \"to\": 1399, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"What was in the past is in the past.\", \"from\": 1400, \"to\": 1436, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I can not change his past.\", \"from\": 1437, \"to\": 1463, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am here to play with him.\", \"from\": 1464, \"to\": 1491, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We want to have good results here.\", \"from\": 1493, \"to\": 1528, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"There are a lot of people who support us.\", \"from\": 1529, \"to\": 1570, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We do it for them.\", \"from\": 1571, \"to\": 1589, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"He has a lot of pressure on his shoulders.\", \"from\": 1591, \"to\": 1634, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am OK with that.\", \"from\": 1635, \"to\": 1653, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Mentally we are strong, I am strong, we will get through this together.\\\"\", \"from\": 1654, \"to\": 1726, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The 23-year-old added: \\\"It is what it is.\", \"from\": 1728, \"to\": 1769, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I was disappointed with the fans.\", \"from\": 1770, \"to\": 1803, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We talked on the field and asked ourselves: what do we need from each other?\", \"from\": 1804, \"to\": 1880, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It was worse than in the first game.\", \"from\": 1881, \"to\": 1917, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We need each other on the field, the hugs, the cheering.\\\"\", \"from\": 1919, \"to\": 1977, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He is not staying at the Olympic Village with his fellow competitors at his own request and will not conduct the usual post-match mixed zone interviews.\", \"from\": 1979, \"to\": 2131, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In a previous interview, Immers was asked if van de Velde had ever expressed any remorse to him for rape, Immers said: \\\"No, he does not, he does not explain it.\\\"\", \"from\": 2133, \"to\": 2294, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2178, \"end\": 2190, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charles_William_Meredith_van_de_Velde\", \"score\": 0.9999786743697067, \"rank\": 2.1326084920168366e-05, \"text\": \"van de Velde\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charles_William_Meredith_van_de_Velde\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charles_William_Meredith_van_de_Velde\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He added: \\\"People are allowed to have an opinion, but we just want to play the\\u00a0tournament as well as possible.\\\"\", \"from\": 2296, \"to\": 2407, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Immers' defence of his teammate comes afterPaula Radcliffe was forced to apologisefor wishing the convicted criminal \\\"the best of luck\\\".\", \"from\": 2409, \"to\": 2545, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2458, \"end\": 2467, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniel_Radcliffe\", \"score\": 0.9490840016613636, \"rank\": 0.053647496851141244, \"text\": \"Radcliffe\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniel_Radcliffe\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniel_Radcliffe\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"His selection for this year's Olympics has been condemned by many, particularly women's safety groups.\", \"from\": 2547, \"to\": 2649, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"However, during an appearance on LBC'sAndrew Marr Tonightshow, former Team GB Olympian Radcliffe suggested he should not be 'punished twice' for his actions.\", \"from\": 2651, \"to\": 2808, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2721, \"end\": 2737, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Team GB Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}, {\"begin\": 2738, \"end\": 2747, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniel_Radcliffe\", \"score\": 0.9490840016613636, \"rank\": 0.053647496851141244, \"text\": \"Radcliffe\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniel_Radcliffe\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniel_Radcliffe\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She said banning Van de Velde from competing at the Olympics was a \\\"very dangerous line to go down, given that we allow people who cheat in sport and take drugs in sport to come back.\\\"\", \"from\": 2810, \"to\": 2994, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She continued: \\\"He served his jail time, and it's a long time to carry on paying for that mistake for the rest of your life.\", \"from\": 2996, \"to\": 3120, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He may well have turned it round and completely repented.\", \"from\": 3121, \"to\": 3178, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I know that he is married now and has settled down.\", \"from\": 3180, \"to\": 3232, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I think it's a tough thing to do to punish him twice and if he's managed to successfully turn his life around after being sent to prison and to qualify and to be playing sport at the highest level, then I actually wish him the best of luck.\\\"\", \"from\": 3233, \"to\": 3474, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Explore more on these topics:  Crime  Dutch  Olympic Games  paris 2024 olympics  paula radcliffe  sensitive  Steven van de Velde  Volleyball  More fromJoe.co.uk  Full list of 59 vehicles facing \\u00a35,690 car tax from April  news  Iran Live: Follow the latest updates on the conflict  news  Warning issued to couples who have sex less than once a week  news  Keir Starmer to hold emergency COBR meeting  news  UK airline falls into administration with all flights cancelled  news  Newsletter coming soon  Back to Top  More  Follow  Contact  \\u00a92026Joe.co.ukor its affiliated companies.\", \"from\": 3476, \"to\": 4055, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3557, \"